title: Quiet Studio --Luxury Furnished Short Term Lakeside $1250/mo
posting_body: ['Available beginning Oct 1st, 2022, short term rental for month to month lease/rent.', 'Ideal for traveling nurse, or other professional, etc.', 'One person occupancy only.', 'On South Lindstrom Lake --some say this is the "best beach on the lake."', 'We certainly have some of the best sunsets!', 'Dock with bench to fish off of or sunbathe.', 'Or, take a friend out on two kayaks out for a relaxing afternoon on the lake.', 'Walk north 1/2 mile, and you arrive in downtown Lindstrom: parks, live music, ice cream, churches, shops and history museum!', 'Walk south 1 1/2 miles, and you arrive at the WildCat Community Center, where a membership gets you access to weight rooms, walking tracking, community classes (pickleball!), and an indoor pool.', 'All utilities included in this rental -- so take long showers!', ' No going to the laundry --as', 'this unit has its own W/D in unit, too!', "Large Studio apartment (19' x 16') includes a queen sized bed, plus a futon (double), night stand, and coffee table, and a full kitchen.", 'As this property has been in the same family for over 100 years, the pictured panels on the long wall under "Lindstrom Stories" outline the heritage and history of some of the founding fathers of the town of Lindstrom.', 'The kitchen includes an eat-at-counter, self-cleaning oven, under-the-counter fridge, 3-in-1 breakfast center which includes coffee maker, toaster oven, and small electric pan.', ' Plus a microwave.', 'Wall mounted vacuum cleaner and wall mounted ironing board, included.', 'Walk out onto a private deck off your kitchen to enjoy your dinner outdoors at the picnic table, or simply bask in the glow of the best sunsets, ever!', 'Wall mounted 43" SMART Roku TV and good Wi-Fi.', 'Large bathroom (12\'6" x 7\') includes double vanities with drawers, large medicine cab, shower/tub, and a separate private toilet room, with your own washer and dryer units.', 'Heated floors in the winter, AC and ceiling fan, in the summer.', 'Pet deposit $90 pet deposit (non-refundable).', 'Refundable $1000 security/damage deposit, reserves it for you.', "One month's rent ($1250) and $190 cleaning fee lets you move in.", 'No smoking indoors or on the premises.', 'Off-street parking available for ONE vehicle.', 'Maximum: Suitable for 1 person (zero exceptions).', 'Accepting applications.', 'All applicants will be screened using FurnishedFinder screening tool.']
